            "description": "These crispy smashed potatoes are a notch above your typical spuds. They’re crunchy on the outside, creamy on the inside, and topped with a savory ginger scallion sauce. Serve as a side dish or appetizer.",
            "name": "Crispy Smashed Potatoes With Ginger Scallion Sauce",
            "seo_title": "",
            "video_id": null,
            "user_ratings": {
                "score": 0.75,
                "count_negative": 1,
                "count_positive": 3
            },
            "brand": null,
            "slug": "crispy-smashed-potatoes-with-ginger-scallion-sauce",
            "prep_time_minutes": 20,
            "created_at": 1658350054,
            "inspired_by_url": null,
            "approved_at": 1658536109,
            "renditions": [],
            "country": "US",
            "instructions": [
                {
                    "id": 72562,
                    "position": 1,
                    "display_text": "Bring a medium pot of water to a boil, then add 1 tablespoon of kosher salt and the potatoes. Cook for 20–25 minutes, until the potatoes are fork-tender. Drain the potatoes in a colander and let cool for 5 minutes, or until safe to handle.",
                    "start_time": 0,
                    "appliance": null,
                    "end_time": 0,
                    "temperature": null
                },
                {
                    "id": 72563,
                    "position": 2,
                    "display_text": "Preheat the oven to 400°F (200°C)..",
                    "start_time": 0,
                    "appliance": "oven",
                    "end_time": 0,
                    "temperature": 400
                },
                {
                    "id": 72564,
                    "position": 3,
                    "display_text": "Transfer the potatoes to a baking sheet and smash using the bottom of a cup or a fork to about ¼ inch thick. Arrange the smashed potatoes in a single layer, then drizzle with the olive oil and season with salt and garlic powder.",
                    "start_time": 0,
                    "appliance": null,
                    "end_time": 0,
                    "temperature": null
                },
                {
                    "position": 4,
                    "display_text": "Roast the potatoes for 40 minutes, flipping once halfway through, until golden brown and crispy.",
                    "start_time": 0,
                    "appliance": null,
                    "end_time": 0,
                    "temperature": null,
                    "id": 72565
                },
                {
                    "appliance": null,
                    "end_time": 0,
                    "temperature": null,
                    "id": 72566,
                    "position": 5,
                    "display_text": "While the potatoes are roasting, make the ginger scallion sauce: Heat the avocado oil in a small saucepan over medium-high heat until the temperature reaches 375°F (190°C).",
                    "start_time": 0
                },
                {
                    "end_time": 0,
                    "temperature": null,
                    "id": 72567,
                    "position": 6,
                    "display_text": "Add the scallions, garlic, ginger and salt to a medium heatproof bowl. Carefully pour the hot oil into the bowl. The mixture will sizzle a lot. Once the aromatics stop sizzling, stir with a spoon until evenly mixed. Set aside until ready to use.",
                    "start_time": 0,
                    "appliance": null
                },
                {
                    "display_text": "To serve, transfer the roasted potatoes to a platter and top with the ginger scallion sauce. Serve immediately.",
                    "start_time": 0,
                    "appliance": null,
                    "end_time": 0,
                    "temperature": null,
                    "id": 72568,
                    "position": 7
                },
                {
                    "end_time": 0,
                    "temperature": null,
                    "id": 72569,
                    "position": 8,
                    "display_text": "Enjoy!",
                    "start_time": 0,
                    "appliance": null
                }
            ],
